<body>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10549" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW"><variable id="macrosecurity_ts"><link href="text/shared/optionen/macrosecurity_ts.xhp">Trusted Sources</link>
</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10567" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Specifies the <link href="text/shared/optionen/macrosecurity.xhp">macro security</link> settings for trusted certificates and trusted file locations.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10578" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Trusted certificates</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1057C" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Lists the trusted certificates.<comment>UFI: scope - for this doc? for all of SO? for the system?</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10591" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="NEW">View</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10595" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the <link href="text/shared/optionen/viewcertificate.xhp">View Certificate</link> dialog for the selected certificate.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105A6" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="NEW">Remove</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105AA" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Removes the selected certificate from the list of trusted certificates.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105AD" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Trusted file locations</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105B1" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Trusted file locations are used only if the security level is set to "very high". With this setting, document macros are only executed if they have been opened from one of the following locations.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105B4" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="NEW">Add</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105B8" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens a folder selection dialog. Select a folder from which all macros are allowed to execute.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105BB" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="NEW">Remove</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105BF" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Removes the selected folder from the list of trusted file locations.</paragraph>
</body>
